#Algorthim for Linear Search
Step1:Start

Step2 :Intalization Array a[n]

step3:accept number from user to be search

step 4:set counter i=0;		

step 5:compare a[i] with number
step 6:if a[i]==num then 
	display number found at i location
	go to step 9
            else 
	i=i+1;
step7 :repeate step 5 and 6 until i<n
step 8:if i==n  then 
	display number is not found
step 9:stop
